What you need to run the application
=====================================

1. Grab the latest version of sbt for your platform (http://www.scala-sbt.org/, at least 0.12.2) and install it
2. Install mongodb (http://www.mongodb.org/)
3. Install OpenOffice (http://www.openoffice.org/)
3. Install nodejs, npm, coffee, less (used as compilers for coffee and less files)

How to start the application
=====================================

1. Don't forget to start the mongo db deamon
2. execute "sbt run" in the project-zoom/ folder